Sentencas: The effect of gas supply method on the performance of a single-chamber solid oxide fuel cell micro-stack and single cells was studied, and a novel gas supply method with separated gas vents in the gas tube was proposed.
Titulo: Effect of gas supply method on the performance of the single-chamber SOFC micro-stack and the single cells

Sentencas: The traditional gas supply method was also investigated for comparison.
Titulo: Effect of gas supply method on the performance of the single-chamber SOFC micro-stack and the single cells

Sentencas: Results showed that the single cells could obtain a uniform open-circuit voltage and power output by using the separated gas supply method.
Titulo: Effect of gas supply method on the performance of the single-chamber SOFC micro-stack and the single cells

Sentencas: For the traditional gas supply method, the cell at the outlet position yielded inferior performance compared to that of the inlet cell.
Titulo: Effect of gas supply method on the performance of the single-chamber SOFC micro-stack and the single cells

Sentencas: The gas flow rate showed a significant effect on the performance of the cells.
Titulo: Effect of gas supply method on the performance of the single-chamber SOFC micro-stack and the single cells

Sentencas: Finally, the stack operated with the separated gas supply method produced a higher power output than that operated with the traditional gas supply method.
Titulo: Effect of gas supply method on the performance of the single-chamber SOFC micro-stack and the single cells
